### ============================================================
### OAuth2 & JWT APIs
### ============================================================

### ----------------------------------------------------------
### OAuth2 로그인 URI 조회 - Google
### ----------------------------------------------------------
GET {{baseUrl}}/oauth/uri/google
Accept: application/json

### ----------------------------------------------------------
### OAuth2 로그인 URI 조회 - Kakao
### ----------------------------------------------------------
GET {{baseUrl}}/oauth/uri/kakao
Accept: application/json

### ----------------------------------------------------------
### OAuth2 로그인 URI 조회 - Apple
### ----------------------------------------------------------
GET {{baseUrl}}/oauth/uri/apple
Accept: application/json

### ----------------------------------------------------------
### OAuth2 콜백 - Google (GET)
### ----------------------------------------------------------
GET {{baseUrl}}/oauth/callback/google?code=auth-code-here&device_type=ANDROID&device_id=device-123
Accept: application/json

### ----------------------------------------------------------
### OAuth2 콜백 - Kakao (GET)
### ----------------------------------------------------------
GET {{baseUrl}}/oauth/callback/kakao?code=auth-code-here&device_type=IOS&device_id=device-456
Accept: application/json

### ----------------------------------------------------------
### OAuth2 콜백 - Apple (POST with id_token)
### ----------------------------------------------------------
POST {{baseUrl}}/oauth/callback/apple?code=auth-code-here&id_token=apple-id-token&device_type=IOS&device_id=device-789
Accept: application/json

### ----------------------------------------------------------
### JWT 토큰 갱신 (Reissue)
### ----------------------------------------------------------
POST {{baseUrl}}/jwt/reissue
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

{
  "refreshToken": "{{refreshToken}}"
}

### ----------------------------------------------------------
### 로그아웃 (현재 세션)
### ----------------------------------------------------------
POST {{baseUrl}}/jwt/logout
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Accept: application/json

### ----------------------------------------------------------
### 전체 로그아웃 (모든 세션)
### ----------------------------------------------------------
POST {{baseUrl}}/jwt/logout-all
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Accept: application/json

### ----------------------------------------------------------
### 활성 세션 목록 조회
### ----------------------------------------------------------
GET {{baseUrl}}/jwt/sessions
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Accept: application/json

### ----------------------------------------------------------
### 토큰 상태 조회
### ----------------------------------------------------------
GET {{baseUrl}}/jwt/token-status
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Accept: application/json
